1
00:00:35,890 --> 00:00:38,470
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,470 --> 00:00:41,310
=Episode 31=

3
00:00:43,625 --> 00:00:45,083
This is the money

4
00:00:45,083 --> 00:00:46,208
the Commander prepared for you.

5
00:00:46,375 --> 00:00:47,666
We will hand it out now,

6
00:00:47,875 --> 00:00:49,208
then you may return home one by one.

7
00:00:53,916 --> 00:00:55,541
Your visit honors us, Young Duke.

8
00:00:55,875 --> 00:00:57,166
You bring light to this humble place.

9
00:00:58,541 --> 00:00:59,625
Your Highness summoned me.

10
00:00:59,958 --> 00:01:00,875
How could I not come?

11
00:01:02,125 --> 00:01:03,250
We grew up together.

12
00:01:03,541 --> 00:01:04,875
Why act so distant, Beiming?

13
00:01:05,083 --> 00:01:06,333
Please, sit.

14
00:01:06,958 --> 00:01:09,458
What does Your Highness require of me?

15
00:01:10,583 --> 00:01:11,375
Require? I would not dare.

16
00:01:12,541 --> 00:01:13,708
About Meizhen House,

17
00:01:13,916 --> 00:01:16,958
Gao Tianxi used my name to do evil

18
00:01:17,416 --> 00:01:18,958
and even offended you.

19
00:01:19,916 --> 00:01:21,208
If he were not already in prison,

20
00:01:21,708 --> 00:01:23,916
I would punish that slave myself.

21
00:01:26,458 --> 00:01:27,083
As for

22
00:01:27,750 --> 00:01:29,458
what Gao Tianxi did,

23
00:01:29,833 --> 00:01:31,416
it truly had nothing to do with me.

24
00:01:31,833 --> 00:01:33,666
I hope this will not

25
00:01:33,875 --> 00:01:35,291
drive a wedge between us.

26
00:01:35,958 --> 00:01:36,750
Your Highness.

27
00:01:37,958 --> 00:01:38,916
You didn't summon me

28
00:01:39,125 --> 00:01:41,458
just to say these harmless little words,
did you?

29
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:45,250
I mainly wished to apologize to you.

30
00:01:51,250 --> 00:01:51,750
I would not dare accept it.

31
00:01:54,125 --> 00:01:56,333
You are a prince. I'm your subject.

32
00:01:57,333 --> 00:01:59,583
How could I accept an apology
from Prince Fu?

33
00:02:00,750 --> 00:02:02,541
From the sound of it,

34
00:02:03,583 --> 00:02:05,583
you are not willing to make peace.

35
00:02:11,791 --> 00:02:13,125
I would like to hear

36
00:02:13,708 --> 00:02:15,166
what Your Highness means

37
00:02:15,791 --> 00:02:16,916
by making peace.

38
00:02:17,875 --> 00:02:20,500
Let the Meizhen House matter end here.

39
00:02:21,083 --> 00:02:22,875
Don't let it spread any further.

40
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,750
Then you should speak
to the Northern Bureau,

41
00:02:31,291 --> 00:02:33,291
not the idlest man in the realm.

42
00:02:33,541 --> 00:02:35,500
Everyone knows the Northern Bureau

43
00:02:35,666 --> 00:02:37,458
takes its cue from the Chang family.

44
00:02:38,041 --> 00:02:40,625
Had your brother
not been gravely wounded,

45
00:02:41,166 --> 00:02:43,750
the post of Northern Bureau Commander

46
00:02:44,375 --> 00:02:47,291
would never have gone to that old man
Zhang Weimin.

47
00:02:47,666 --> 00:02:48,208
Prince Fu.

48
00:02:49,875 --> 00:02:50,625
Watch your words.

49
00:02:51,083 --> 00:02:51,791
Young Duke.

50
00:02:53,125 --> 00:02:54,708
I came in good faith today

51
00:02:55,583 --> 00:02:57,541
to turn an enemy into a friend.

52
00:02:58,458 --> 00:02:59,791
Your Highness summoned me here,

53
00:02:59,958 --> 00:03:00,958
and now I understand why.

54
00:03:02,833 --> 00:03:03,500
I will

55
00:03:04,041 --> 00:03:04,833
take my leave.

56
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,541
Wait.

57
00:03:11,333 --> 00:03:12,583
Since this is an apology,

58
00:03:13,041 --> 00:03:14,791
I should show some sincerity.

59
00:03:15,875 --> 00:03:17,750
I have known music since childhood.

60
00:03:18,291 --> 00:03:21,916
Allow me to play a piece for you myself

61
00:03:21,916 --> 00:03:23,250
as a gesture of goodwill.

62
00:03:33,291 --> 00:03:34,041
Help!

63
00:03:34,625 --> 00:03:35,375
Run!

64
00:03:39,541 --> 00:03:40,291
Taozi.

65
00:05:15,125 --> 00:05:16,541
Your Highness, I'll take my leave.

66
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,810
(Prince Fu's Manor)

67
00:05:34,583 --> 00:05:35,083
Guys.

68
00:05:35,791 --> 00:05:36,625
This is a private action.

69
00:05:37,375 --> 00:05:38,166
Anyone unwilling to join

70
00:05:38,375 --> 00:05:39,208
may step back now.

71
00:05:41,166 --> 00:05:42,166
We follow you!

72
00:06:09,333 --> 00:06:09,958
Why are you here?

73
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:11,041
Young Master Chang sent me.

74
00:06:11,416 --> 00:06:13,583
Don't worry. No one will hurt you
while I'm here.

75
00:06:15,791 --> 00:06:16,583
Guan Yunfeng.

76
00:06:17,208 --> 00:06:18,125
You have a death wish.

77
00:06:18,166 --> 00:06:18,750
It's you.

78
00:06:19,625 --> 00:06:20,208
You know him?

79
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:21,083
He is a Qianhu

80
00:06:21,083 --> 00:06:22,458
under Commander Wang Yan
of the Five Armies Command.

81
00:06:22,708 --> 00:06:23,083
He's Du Bin.

82
00:06:23,541 --> 00:06:24,208
Guys.

83
00:06:24,958 --> 00:06:27,291
Time for a massacre.

84
00:06:27,833 --> 00:06:28,583
Then we fight!

85
00:06:29,958 --> 00:06:30,541
Guan Yunfeng.

86
00:06:31,583 --> 00:06:34,000
As a fifth-rank Qianhu,

87
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,583
I order you

88
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,416
and your men

89
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,166
to lay down your weapons at once

90
00:06:38,333 --> 00:06:39,416
and get out of this villa.

91
00:06:39,708 --> 00:06:41,375
I joined the Enforcement Division

92
00:06:41,666 --> 00:06:42,958
to uphold justice

93
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,666
and protect the weak.

94
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:47,000
(Command Token)
If keeping this eighth-rank post

95
00:06:47,291 --> 00:06:48,500
means joining scum like you,

96
00:06:49,125 --> 00:06:51,041
then I don't need the post!

97
00:06:51,916 --> 00:06:52,625
We don't need it!

98
00:06:52,625 --> 00:06:54,500
Are you making enemies
of imperial officers?

99
00:06:54,708 --> 00:06:55,500
As long as I'm here,

100
00:06:55,916 --> 00:06:57,750
you will not touch a hair
on those girls' heads.

101
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,541
Guys.

102
00:06:58,958 --> 00:06:59,458
Get them!

103
00:06:59,833 --> 00:07:01,250
Kill them!

104
00:07:20,083 --> 00:07:20,791
Taozi. Watch out!

105
00:08:12,583 --> 00:08:13,166
Guan!

106
00:08:16,333 --> 00:08:16,875
Constable Guan.

107
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,708
Surround them all.

108
00:08:24,958 --> 00:08:25,541
Yes!

109
00:08:30,583 --> 00:08:30,875
Trying to run?

110
00:08:31,166 --> 00:08:31,583
Fine.

111
00:08:31,833 --> 00:08:33,750
Find something and burn this place down.

112
00:08:33,958 --> 00:08:34,458
Yes!

113
00:08:37,208 --> 00:08:37,625
Guan.

114
00:08:37,791 --> 00:08:38,375
Guan.

115
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:39,625
You will be fine.

116
00:08:40,791 --> 00:08:41,458
I'm sorry.

117
00:08:42,541 --> 00:08:44,083
I can't protect you anymore.

118
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,333
You have nowhere left to run.

119
00:08:50,333 --> 00:08:52,140
(Poised and Serene)

120
00:08:52,375 --> 00:08:53,166
You will be fine.

121
00:08:54,208 --> 00:08:54,833
Bingfan.

122
00:08:56,166 --> 00:08:56,583
Leng Xin...

123
00:08:57,708 --> 00:08:58,541
I'll catch him.

124
00:08:59,333 --> 00:09:00,166
In the next life,

125
00:09:02,166 --> 00:09:02,666
I will...

126
00:09:05,333 --> 00:09:07,250
I will protect you properly.

127
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,125
Leng Xin.

128
00:09:23,916 --> 00:09:24,500
Guan!

129
00:09:25,625 --> 00:09:26,291
Guan!

130
00:09:29,541 --> 00:09:30,625
Guan!

131
00:09:32,083 --> 00:09:33,291
Guan!

132
00:09:33,875 --> 00:09:34,916
Guan!

133
00:09:43,541 --> 00:09:44,208
Constable Guan!

134
00:09:44,666 --> 00:09:45,291
Constable Guan!

135
00:09:48,333 --> 00:09:48,916
Duoyu.

136
00:09:50,541 --> 00:09:51,125
Open the door.

137
00:09:55,416 --> 00:09:57,166
Avenge Guan!

138
00:10:22,375 --> 00:10:23,375
Die!

139
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:25,333
You scum!

140
00:10:27,875 --> 00:10:29,416
Avenge Guan!

141
00:10:31,875 --> 00:10:32,875
Die!

142
00:10:38,166 --> 00:10:39,625
Die!

143
00:10:40,458 --> 00:10:41,166
Take this!

144
00:10:43,041 --> 00:10:44,041
You murderers!

145
00:10:50,833 --> 00:10:51,541
You scum!

146
00:10:51,833 --> 00:10:53,291
We won't let you get away with this!

147
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,416
Surround them.

148
00:10:55,875 --> 00:10:56,541
Hold them!

149
00:10:56,916 --> 00:10:57,875
Die!

150
00:10:57,916 --> 00:10:58,500
Are you all right?

151
00:10:58,708 --> 00:10:59,458
Beiming.

152
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:01,291
Guan died fighting.

153
00:11:10,208 --> 00:11:11,958
(Your servant Chang Beiming,)

154
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:14,000
(Jinyiwei and heir to Duke Zheng,)

155
00:11:14,916 --> 00:11:16,708
(together with Zhang Weimin,)

156
00:11:16,708 --> 00:11:17,875
(Commander of the Jinyiwei
Northern Bureau,)

157
00:11:18,125 --> 00:11:19,166
(submits this report in full truth.)

158
00:11:20,083 --> 00:11:20,916
(The Meizhen House case)

159
00:11:21,041 --> 00:11:22,000
(was nearing its conclusion.)

160
00:11:22,458 --> 00:11:22,875
(Yet)

161
00:11:23,166 --> 00:11:25,000
(the guilty officials,
desperate to escape punishment,)

162
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:28,000
(colluded with the imprisoned Gao Tianxi)

163
00:11:28,208 --> 00:11:29,125
(to assassinate the witnesses)

164
00:11:29,291 --> 00:11:30,375
(and cover their crimes.)

165
00:11:31,458 --> 00:11:32,916
(Officers from the Five Armies Command)

166
00:11:33,333 --> 00:11:34,291
(posed as assassins)

167
00:11:34,541 --> 00:11:36,625
(and raided Duke Zheng's villa
outside the capital.)

168
00:11:37,125 --> 00:11:39,291
(Their methods were brutal,
meant to silence every witness.)

169
00:11:40,250 --> 00:11:42,541
(The Jinyiwei and Enforcement Division
mounted a desperate defense.)

170
00:11:43,125 --> 00:11:44,875
(Eighth-rank constable Guan Yunfeng)

171
00:11:44,875 --> 00:11:45,708
(fell in the line of duty.)

172
00:11:46,333 --> 00:11:48,041
(This case has shaken the realm)

173
00:11:48,041 --> 00:11:48,875
(and set public anger aflame.)

174
00:11:49,083 --> 00:11:50,666
(Without a full investigation,
the people will not be satisfied.)

175
00:11:51,125 --> 00:11:52,541
(We humbly request that Your Majesty)

176
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:55,291
(order the Cabinet to reopen
the Meizhen House case,)

177
00:11:55,625 --> 00:11:56,875
(to calm the realm)

178
00:11:57,041 --> 00:11:58,625
（and answer the people's grievance.)

179
00:12:00,458 --> 00:12:01,083
So it has reached the throne.

180
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,000
These are the fine officials
you have trained for me?

181
00:12:05,166 --> 00:12:06,583
We failed in our oversight.

182
00:12:07,208 --> 00:12:09,541
We deserve death.

183
00:12:10,166 --> 00:12:15,583
Ye has already taken to his sickbed
in fear.

184
00:12:16,541 --> 00:12:19,458
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty.

185
00:12:19,666 --> 00:12:21,791
The court is in an uproar,

186
00:12:22,541 --> 00:12:24,291
and the people are crying out
for justice.

187
00:12:26,625 --> 00:12:27,958
How shall we handle it?

188
00:12:32,541 --> 00:12:34,416
Wang Yan of the Five Armies Command

189
00:12:35,291 --> 00:12:36,708
is to be sent to the Imperial Prison
for trial.

190
00:12:37,083 --> 00:12:38,541
Marquis Taiping, Yin Xian,

191
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:40,625
has committed monstrous crimes.

192
00:12:41,541 --> 00:12:43,291
Behead him to answer the people's anger.

193
00:12:44,333 --> 00:12:46,583
Gao Tianxi is beyond pardon.

194
00:12:47,708 --> 00:12:49,166
Execute him at once.

195
00:12:49,458 --> 00:12:51,333
All other officials involved

196
00:12:51,833 --> 00:12:53,375
are to be dismissed and exiled.

197
00:12:56,208 --> 00:12:57,583
And the last one?

198
00:12:58,791 --> 00:13:00,375
What shall be done with him?

199
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:02,625
Your Majesty's judgment is wise.

200
00:13:03,666 --> 00:13:04,416
Do your job.

201
00:13:04,875 --> 00:13:07,166
We obey.

202
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:14,000
(Serve the Public, Uphold the Law)

203
00:13:14,791 --> 00:13:16,640
(Serve the Public, Uphold the Law)

204
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:18,666
Bring out Yin Xian!

205
00:13:19,541 --> 00:13:20,583
Kill him!

206
00:13:20,791 --> 00:13:22,875
Kill him!

207
00:13:22,875 --> 00:13:23,958
(Serve the Public, Uphold the Law)
Kill him!

208
00:13:24,041 --> 00:13:24,875
Beast!

209
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:26,666
(Execute)

210
00:13:26,666 --> 00:13:27,666
(Execute)
He preyed on the people!

211
00:13:28,166 --> 00:13:29,541
(Execute)
Rid the people of this evil!

212
00:13:29,625 --> 00:13:30,041
Execute.

213
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:30,930
(Execute)

214
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:32,640
(Serve the Public, Uphold the Law)

215
00:13:34,250 --> 00:13:35,666
Good!

216
00:13:35,666 --> 00:13:37,333
Good!

217
00:13:38,541 --> 00:13:39,541
Bring out Gao Tianxi.

218
00:13:40,958 --> 00:13:42,125
Go to hell!

219
00:13:42,541 --> 00:13:44,375
(Silence)
Kill him!

220
00:13:44,375 --> 00:13:50,100
Kill him!

221
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:57,083
Kill him!

222
00:13:57,083 --> 00:13:58,208
(Execute)
Kill him!

223
00:13:58,208 --> 00:14:02,958
Kill him!

224
00:14:02,958 --> 00:14:03,666
(Execute: Condemned Prisoner Gao Tianxi)
Kill him!

225
00:14:03,666 --> 00:14:05,000
Kill him!

226
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,250
Mom, I'm hungry.

227
00:14:07,875 --> 00:14:08,666
Execute.

228
00:14:08,770 --> 00:14:09,470
(Execute)

229
00:14:11,583 --> 00:14:13,000
Good! Good!

230
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,458
Good! Good!

231
00:14:14,458 --> 00:14:15,833
He deserved it!

232
00:14:15,833 --> 00:14:18,458
Good! Good!

233
00:14:18,458 --> 00:14:20,000
He deserved it!

234
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:20,666
Mother!

235
00:14:20,666 --> 00:14:21,166
Your Highness!

236
00:14:21,166 --> 00:14:21,583
Mother!

237
00:14:21,583 --> 00:14:22,083
Your Highness!

238
00:14:22,083 --> 00:14:23,333
Save me, Mother!

239
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:25,125
Mother! Mother!

240
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:26,416
Help!

241
00:14:28,333 --> 00:14:29,625
Your Highness, you dropped something.

242
00:14:29,625 --> 00:14:30,333
Mother!

243
00:14:30,375 --> 00:14:32,958
Our son is young. He is still a child.

244
00:14:33,125 --> 00:14:34,166
He was led astray

245
00:14:34,416 --> 00:14:35,625
and made a terrible mistake.

246
00:14:35,875 --> 00:14:38,583
Your Majesty, please show him mercy.

247
00:14:38,791 --> 00:14:40,208
You keep saying he is young,

248
00:14:40,791 --> 00:14:41,833
that he is still a child.

249
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:44,958
When a child goes untaught,
the fault lies with the parents.

250
00:14:45,666 --> 00:14:47,000
He became what he is today.

251
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:49,333
Do you bear no blame at all?

252
00:14:50,125 --> 00:14:50,708
Your Majesty.

253
00:14:51,458 --> 00:14:52,666
I know my fault.

254
00:14:53,625 --> 00:14:56,291
Please, for our son's sake,

255
00:14:57,083 --> 00:14:58,708
spare him this time.

256
00:14:58,875 --> 00:15:00,916
Even if I spare him, will Heaven
spare him?

257
00:15:01,958 --> 00:15:03,625
Will the people spare him?

258
00:15:04,291 --> 00:15:06,000
Will history spare him?

259
00:15:07,416 --> 00:15:08,875
Have mercy, Your Majesty!

260
00:15:10,291 --> 00:15:11,083
I know

261
00:15:11,958 --> 00:15:12,583
that for years,

262
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:15,083
he has coveted the Crown Prince's place.

263
00:15:15,583 --> 00:15:16,916
He built Meizhen House,

264
00:15:17,416 --> 00:15:18,333
colluded with court officials,

265
00:15:18,708 --> 00:15:19,625
and gathered factions for himself.

266
00:15:21,291 --> 00:15:23,458
Was it not all to seize
the heir's place?

267
00:15:24,083 --> 00:15:25,875
But he has gone too far.

268
00:15:26,541 --> 00:15:27,416
Next spring,

269
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:29,750
send him to his fief.

270
00:15:30,458 --> 00:15:31,958
He is never to enter the capital again
without my decree.

271
00:15:32,083 --> 00:15:32,875
Your Majesty!

272
00:15:33,666 --> 00:15:35,958
I have already shown him mercy
beyond the law!

273
00:15:36,458 --> 00:15:38,125
I obey.

274
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,791
Leave.

275
00:15:41,375 --> 00:15:43,291
(Righteous and Unyielding)
So the Meizhen House case just ends?

276
00:15:43,833 --> 00:15:45,791
Then Guan Yunfeng died for nothing.

277
00:15:45,875 --> 00:15:48,208
Marquis Taiping and Gao Tianxi are dead.

278
00:15:48,208 --> 00:15:49,000
What more do you want?

279
00:15:49,375 --> 00:15:50,500
Those two beasts' lives

280
00:15:51,041 --> 00:15:52,541
don't make up
for one good person's life.

281
00:15:52,541 --> 00:15:52,875
You...

282
00:15:52,875 --> 00:15:53,916
Enough, enough.

283
00:15:54,375 --> 00:15:55,083
Both of you, stop.

284
00:15:56,416 --> 00:15:59,125
This case has already shaken
the whole court.

285
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:02,250
More than 20 senior officials

286
00:16:02,333 --> 00:16:03,916
have been dismissed and exiled.

287
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:06,750
Now even a prince has been dragged
into it.

288
00:16:06,958 --> 00:16:09,500
But Prince Fu is the true mastermind
behind Meizhen House.

289
00:16:09,875 --> 00:16:12,666
Do you have solid proof
against Prince Fu?

290
00:16:13,166 --> 00:16:13,958
Do you?

291
00:16:15,583 --> 00:16:17,166
You slippery old fixer.

292
00:16:17,625 --> 00:16:18,125
Hey!

293
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:19,166
Wait!

294
00:16:19,666 --> 00:16:20,583
What did you just say?

295
00:16:21,833 --> 00:16:23,041
What is that supposed to mean?

296
00:16:23,416 --> 00:16:24,875
Are you defying me?

297
00:16:25,250 --> 00:16:27,666
Do you want me to dismiss you?

298
00:16:28,166 --> 00:16:29,583
Yes. Dismiss her.

299
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,291
I will dismiss you first!

300
00:16:31,416 --> 00:16:31,666
Me?

301
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:33,375
Look at what she has become.

302
00:16:33,916 --> 00:16:35,375
This is what happens
when you indulge her.

303
00:16:36,875 --> 00:16:37,666
So now it is my fault?

304
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:51,140
(Grave of Guan Yunfeng)

305
00:16:52,583 --> 00:16:53,250
Guan.

306
00:16:53,250 --> 00:16:54,770
(Grave of Guan Yunfeng)

307
00:16:55,333 --> 00:16:56,708
I will avenge you.

308
00:17:04,208 --> 00:17:04,750
Shen Bingfan.

309
00:17:05,333 --> 00:17:06,208
Drinking yourself into the ground

310
00:17:06,375 --> 00:17:07,500
won't bring him back.

311
00:17:08,791 --> 00:17:09,833
I hate myself.

312
00:17:10,125 --> 00:17:11,166
I can't avenge him.

313
00:17:11,708 --> 00:17:12,541
Our enemy

314
00:17:14,041 --> 00:17:15,458
is a prince of the blood.

315
00:17:17,041 --> 00:17:18,458
We can't rush this.

316
00:17:20,333 --> 00:17:21,833
I thought once I became Jinyiwei,

317
00:17:22,416 --> 00:17:23,666
I could uphold justice.

318
00:17:24,833 --> 00:17:25,666
Now I see,

319
00:17:26,041 --> 00:17:27,041
it was all a lie.

320
00:17:27,916 --> 00:17:28,833
So you are afraid.

321
00:17:29,250 --> 00:17:30,458
I'm heartbroken.

322
00:17:30,458 --> 00:17:31,875
So you are giving up on yourself?

323
00:17:33,666 --> 00:17:34,791
Are you still going after Leng Xin?

324
00:17:36,333 --> 00:17:38,916
What if Leng Xin also has a prince
behind him?

325
00:17:39,916 --> 00:17:41,458
What can we possibly do to him?

326
00:17:44,208 --> 00:17:45,833
All they need is a scapegoat.

327
00:17:47,041 --> 00:17:48,916
Then every grave crime
becomes a minor matter.

328
00:17:49,958 --> 00:17:52,458
Even Jinyiwei files can be altered
at will.

329
00:17:53,041 --> 00:17:54,875
That is how my father was sacrificed.

330
00:18:01,375 --> 00:18:01,958
Beiming.

331
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,583
Right now, it hurts so much.

332
00:18:07,791 --> 00:18:09,958
I don't want to hunt murderers anymore

333
00:18:10,541 --> 00:18:11,750
or search for Leng Xin.

334
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,083
I just want to go home.

335
00:18:20,666 --> 00:18:21,375
What about me?

336
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:25,875
Where does that leave me?

337
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:45,190
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

338
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:48,940
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

339
00:18:49,190 --> 00:18:52,190
♪My heart drifted lost♪

340
00:18:52,190 --> 00:18:55,600
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

341
00:18:56,690 --> 00:18:59,900
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

342
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:03,650
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

343
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:06,440
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

344
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:10,480
♪I've softly let it go♪

345
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:14,350
♪The vow you made was true♪

346
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:18,100
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

347
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:20,310
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

348
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:24,850
♪And forget at world's end♪

349
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:26,650
♪Embracing memory♪

350
00:19:26,650 --> 00:19:29,020
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

351
00:19:29,020 --> 00:19:32,900
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

352
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:35,230
♪I wish to let it pass♪

353
00:19:35,230 --> 00:19:40,230
♪And run toward this vast life♪
